<p>Hello <%= @resource.name %>!</p>

<p>Someone asked Offbott to change your password, and you can do this through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @resource.reset_password_token) %></p>

<p>If you didn't ask for this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you click the link above and create a new one.</p>
